1. *Rane* su ga bolele kada je hodao. (The wounds hurt him when he was walking.) 
2. On često posmatra *rane* koje je nanela rat. (He often observes the wounds caused by the war.)
3. Oni su izliječili njegove *rane*. (They healed his wounds.)
4. On je imao duboke i bolne *rane*. (He had deep and painful wounds.)
5. Zvijezde su se smještale na nebu kao *rane*. (The stars were placed in the sky like wounds.) 
6. *Rane* su se zacijelile nakon nekoliko dana. (The wounds healed after a few days.) 
7. On je liječio svoje *rane*. (He was treating his wounds.)
8. On je osjećao bol u *ranama*. (He felt pain in his wounds.)